Create Both
Remove Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount photocarl
Host imap.fastmail.com
Port 993
User carlf@carlf.io
PassCmd "~/bin/get_password imap.fastmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore photocarl-remote
Account photocarl
UseNamespace yes

MaildirStore photocarl-local
Path ~/Mail/photocarl/
Inbox ~/Mail/photocarl/INBOX
AltMap no
Flatten .

Channel photocarl
Master :photocarl-remote:
Slave :photocarl-local:
Patterns *
Expunge Both
